      "title": "CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)",
      "properties": {
        "cnr_id": "comfy-core",
        "ver": "0.3.45",
        "Node name for S&R": "CLIPTextEncode",
        "widget_ue_connectable": {}
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "Create a dramatic, classical impasto painting with a strong touch of abstract expressionism. A woman with a wild, flowing bordeaux-red mane stands on the edge of a perilous cliff — her symmetrical beautiful face turned slightly downward, eyes downcast, radiating mystery and emotional weight. She has muscular arms and blight skin, wearing a dark charcoal dress with dramatic ruching and draping that clings to her form — suggesting both elegance and vulnerability. The background is rough, textured, and abstracted — rocky cliffs rendered in thick, gestural brushstrokes, using only shades of black, white, and gray to create stark contrast with her vibrant red hair. The entire composition is defined by visible, heavy paint application — thick impasto textures, bold strokes, emotional intensity. Lighting is dramatic but painterly — not photographic — with deep shadows and luminous highlights achieved through layered color and texture.  classic oil painting meets abstract expressionism — think Van Gogh meets Willem de Kooning. Embrace imperfection, gesture, and emotional rawness. The painting tells a story — silent, powerful, waiting to be felt.\nStyle: Impasto Style, Expressive Art, Dramatic Portraiture, Heavy Brushwork, Diagonal Composition, Figurative Expressionism.\nBackground: minimal, atmospheric, focused on the cliff and sky — no distracting elements.",
        [
          false,
          true
        ]
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
    },
